1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with vehicle re-identification based on image classification, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses deep neural networks for training and classification, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The use of deep neural networks for image classification and re-identification can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with analyzing video data, which is a form of multimedia. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves the retrieval of information from images and videos, which can be considered as a subfield of information retrieval.
